      <!-- About Us -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8">About Us</h3>
        <div class="text-gray-600 space-y-4">
          <p>We are a new tour & travel company established in 2024. Our home base is located in Probolinggo, East Java, as this is where we grew up and it is very close to the famous volcanic tourist attraction, Mount Bromo.</p>
          
          <p>Although our company is relatively young, our mentors are highly experienced individuals in the fields of transportation, hospitality, and travel management. On average, our mentors have been involved in the travel industry for over 15 years. Some of us are the second generation of our senior mentors.</p>
          
          <p>Currently, we operate tour packages to Yogyakarta (Borobudur, Prambanan, Jomblang Cave, Ijo Temple, etc.), Mount Bromo, Mount Ijen, Tumpak Sewu Waterfall, the Magical Forest of Djawatan, and Lovina Dolphin Beach. In the future, our target is to offer tour packages to Komodo Island.</p>
          
          <p>For tour package prices, we offer very reasonable rates and it is best to discuss further when you have a combination of the Mount Bromo package with other tourist attractions. Our offers on this website are for standard tour classes. For economical or exclusive packages or if you have any other questions, you can contact us via WhatsApp, WeChat, social media private messages, or email.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <!-- How to Find Us -->
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-24">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-8">How to Find Us</h3>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Map placeholder (you can replace with an actual map) -->
        <div class="bg-gray-100 h-80">
          <iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3953.4349113741896!2d113.21332277575787!3d-7.743607776768138!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x2dd7adee168f6749%3A0xd18183f3db6edcc2!2sAlun-Alun%20Kota%20Probolinggo!5e0!3m2!1sen!2sus!4v1742331135502!5m2!1sen!2sus" width="600" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Directions -->
        <div>
          <h4 class="text-xl font-medium mb-6">Our meeting point is Alun - Alun Kota Probolinggo (Town Square)</h4>
          <ol class="space-y-3 text-gray-600 list-decimal list-outside pl-5">
            <li>Head east towards Pasar Mangunharjo (many people refer this market as Pasar Babian)</li>
            <li>Continue east until you reach an intersection</li>
            <li>Please turn left, then now you are in the Arum Permai Residential Area</li>
            <li>Continue north</li>
            <li>You will find a second intersection</li>
            <li>Please turn left into a dead-end alley</li>
            <li>Our location is on the right, two houses after the dead-end intersection</li>
          </ol>
          
          <div class="mt-8 py-4 px-6 bg-[#F68712]/5">
            <p class="text-gray-700">
              <span class="font-medium">Alternatively:</span> Please contact us via WhatsApp or WeChat number. We are always ready to assist you.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
